{
  "stem": "1975.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And ultimately, when I was nine, I have been sent to live together with my grandparents on my father's side to the capital of Kovno.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there, I was-- I started in the Hebrew gymnasium, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at the age of nine-- between nine and 10.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a governmental employee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he was actually by being-- have-- having-- he fought for the independence of Lithuania, and he was given a governmental job, which was a insurance inspector.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And besides that, we also had a factory manufacturing roof paper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My street address in Rakiszki was [NON-ENGLISH]-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means the [NON-ENGLISH], the street number eight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a boy, I belonged to the Boy Scouts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I belonged to the Hashomer Hatzair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And ultimately, I belonged to the Betar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Life was very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As you know, the city, it was not-- it was a small city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And most of the inhabitants were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Lithuanians, the non-Jews, have lived in the surroundings in the small villages surrounding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Rakiszki, there were, like, 60% or 65% of Jews who lived and who have conducted the business.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as a young boy, when I grew up, we had a very nice social life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a Jewish bank.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had different Jewish organizations, organizations who were social organizations, taking care of the less fortunate of those people who were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not too wealthy, and those people who were sick.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had also a hospital in our city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a very social and a very nice life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Especially the Jewish families had a bind between themselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We used to visit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We used to have conferences, lectures.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in a certain way, life was very desirable.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
